# Unreal Engine binary/content assets — tracked via Git LFS.
# Free tier is 10 GiB storage + 10 GiB bandwidth per month, per-account (not per-repo).
# Set the LFS spending budget to $0 in GitHub billing settings so this fails safe instead of billing — see docs/SessionHandoff.md.

